date.headline: 1248. African elephant- Live one
date.text: This one is a real live elephant in Disney Animal World, Orlando, Florida. Unlike asian elephants these are not usually tame. They retain their wild characteristics even in captivity

date.headline: New Elephant Calf
date.text: The ABQ BioPark Zoo welcomed a new elephant calf early the morning of Oct. 2. The female calf and mother, Rozie, are behind-the-scenes bonding. www.abqbiopark.com/elephants
